high_descs: Turn around and go near the TV stand.
Take the potato from the stand.
Turn around and go near the microwave.
Put the potato into the microwave.
Then take it out and go near the sink.
Put the potato on the sink table.
anns.task_desc: Placed the potato on the sink table.

high_descs: Turn right, walk and again turn right and walk, then turn left and head to the tv stand.
Pick up the potato in front of the apple from the tv stand.
Turn right and walk across the chairs and enter into the kitchen, turn right, walk and turn right, head to the microwave.
Put the potato into the microwave and heat it up, then pick it up back.
Turn back and head to the sink counter.
Put the potato on the left down corner of the sink counter top.
anns.task_desc: Put the potato on the sink counter top.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the tv stand.
Head around and walk towards the microwave in the kitchen.
Put the potato inside and pick it back after few seconds.
Place the potato near the sink.
anns.task_desc: To place the potato near the sink.
